            "title": "给2026投资上一道“保险”：美股铂金答疑会员新年礼遇开启",
            "id": 984815,
            "description": "<div class=\"centerarticle\">\n <p>2026开年即风暴： <a class=\"_internal_link_\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.fx168news.com/info/001007/001007002\">美联储</a>主席鲍威尔遭遇前所未有的刑事调查，白宫触手伸向委内瑞拉与格陵兰，伊朗抗议活动愈演愈烈，<a class=\"_internal_link_\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.fx168news.com/info/001003/001003001\">美股</a>再刷新历史新高。</p>\n <p>在金融信用受损、地缘规则重塑的当下，你缺的不是消息，而是决策的底气。</p>\n <h4 id=\"2ajks\"><strong><span style=\"color:#c0392b\">FX168 铂金答疑会员</span></strong></h4>\n <table>\n  <tbody>\n   <tr>\n    <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><strong>会员级别</strong></td>\n    <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><strong>收费标准</strong></td>\n    <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><strong>核心价值</strong></td>\n    <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><strong>适合人群</strong></td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"line-height:1.15\"><strong>月度·尝鲜派</strong></span></td>\n    <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><strong>￥228</strong></td>\n    <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"line-height:1.15\">一顿火锅钱，开启 30 天私人分析师陪伴模式</span></td>\n    <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"line-height:1.15\">观望中，想体验“优先答疑”快感的投资者</span></td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"line-height:1.15\"><strong>半年·实战派</strong></span></td>\n    <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"line-height:1.15\"><strong>￥1250</strong></span></td>\n    <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"line-height:1.15\">6 个月超长陪伴，覆盖 2026 Q1 所有核心节点</span></td>\n    <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"line-height:1.15\">追求稳健、拒绝短期波动的深度玩家</span></td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"line-height:1.15\"><strong>年度·领航派</strong></span></td>\n    <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"line-height:1.15\"><strong>￥2400</strong></span></td>\n    <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"line-height:1.15\">日均仅 ¥6.6，锁定全年的财富安全</span></td>\n    <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"line-height: