168news.com/\">FX168财经</a>网站或APP端观看直播与参与互动。</p>\n <p>2）付款完成后，请添加客服微信，并发送付款截图、团购人员信息及您的FX168用户名，便于客服核验并为您延长对应会员权益。</p>\n <div class=\"braft-img-container\" data-src=\"https://static.fx168api.com/img/user/e7480e51ba115b2a34770fa4628fbdfa/outside1768348384735\" data-alt=\"\"><img src=\"https://static.fx168api.com/img/user/e7480e51ba115b2a34770fa4628fbdfa/outside1768348384735\" alt=\"\">\n </div>\n <h4 id=\"2c77q\"><strong><span style=\"color:#c0392b\">YouTube会员加入方式</span></strong></h4>\n <p>方式A【浏览器】：进入<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@FX168\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"bf-link\">FX168 美国股市频道</a>，点击 <strong>“加入“或”Join”按钮</strong>。友情提示：由于YouTube渠道限制，iOS版YouTube App通常无法直接开通会员，建议通过手机/电脑浏览器进入频道页面进行订阅。</p>\n <div class=\"braft-img-container\" data-src=\"https://static.fx168api.com/img/user/e7480e51ba115b2a34770fa4628fbdfa/outside1768338250488\" data-alt=\"\"><img src=\"https://static.fx168api.com/img/user/e7480e51ba115b2a34770fa4628fbdfa/outside1768338250488\" alt=\"\">\n </div>\n <p>方式B【安卓App】：进入<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@FX168\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"bf-link\">FX168 美国股市频道</a>，点击 <strong>“加入/Join”</strong>。</p>\n <h4 id=\"flnh5\"><strong><span style=\"color:#c0392b\">YouTube会员升级（已有等级用户）</span></strong></h4>\n <p>1. 进入<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@FX168\" target=\"_blank\">FX168美国股市频道主页</a></p>\n <p>2. 点击 “加入“或”Join”按钮（已是会员则显示“查看等级”）</p>\n <p>3. 选择更高档位（如白银→铂金）</p>\n <p>4. 确认支付（系统按差价或下周期收取新费用）</p>\n <p><span style=\"font-size:12px\">备注：以上福利不可叠加使用，FX168财经集团保留最终解释权。</span></p>\n</div>\n<script src=\"https://static.fx168api.com/js/jquery-1.12.3.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://static.fx168api.com/js/fx168_ny_addad.js?t=202409051358\"></script>\n<div style=\"\n    border-top: 1px solid #ddd;\n    margin: 0.3rem 0.2rem 0;\n    padding-bottom: 0.2rem;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    color: #333;\n    font-size:16px;\n    line-height:2;\n\">\n <div>\n  1. 欢迎转载，转载时请标明来源为FX168财经。商业性转载需事先获得授权，请发邮件至：media@fx168group.com。\n </div>\n <div>\n  2. 所有内容仅供参考，不代表FX168财经